com.viaoa.jfc.control

Class OAJfcController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.hub.HubListenerAdapter
      • com.viaoa.jfc.control.OAJfcController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.viaoa.hub.HubListener, EventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AutoCompleteTextFieldController, ButtonController, ComboBoxController, CustomComboBoxController, DateChooserController, FormattedTextFieldController, HTMLTextPaneController, LabelController, ListController, OAImagePanelController, TextAreaController, TextFieldController, ToggleButtonController

    public class OAJfcController
extends com.viaoa.hub.HubListenerAdapter
    Base controller class for OA JFC/Swing components. Implements the HubListener and provides most of the methods required for creating controller Classes (Model/View/Controller) for UI components.

    • Constructor Detail

      • OAJfcController

        public OAJfcController(com.viaoa.hub.Hub hub,
                       Object object,
                       String propertyPath,
                       JComponent comp,
                       com.viaoa.hub.HubChangeListener.Type type,
                       boolean bUseLinkHub,
                       boolean bUseEditQuery)
        Create new controller for Hub and Jfc component
        Parameters:
        hub -
        object - if hub is null, then this object will be put in temp hub and made the AO
        propertyPath - property used by component
        bAoOnly - should controller listen to propChange for all objects in hub, or just AO.
        comp -
        type - default type of change listener
        bUseLinkHub - should setup also include setting up the link hub
        bUseEditQuery - use editQuery to determine enabled/visibl.
